org.hibernate.engine.spi

Interface SessionFactoryImplementor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.io.Closeable, javax.persistence.EntityManagerFactory, HibernateEntityManagerFactory, Mapping, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver, javax.naming.Referenceable, java.io.Serializable, SessionFactory
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SessionFactoryDelegatingImpl, SessionFactoryImpl

    public interface SessionFactoryImplementor
extends Mapping, SessionFactory, QueryParameterBindingTypeResolver
    Defines the internal contract between the SessionFactory and other parts of Hibernate such as implementors of Type.
    See Also:
    SessionFactory, SessionFactoryImpl
